{
  "stem": "4513.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was pretty much the relationships that we had was a family relationship because the people in the neighborhood we just very seldom-- that was one-- I don't how we got to know, but there was another man who my mother and father got to know from somewhere, who was from India.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he used to come and have lunch with-- dinner with us on Sunday many times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a very close friend of the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's about the only person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kids we knew, I got to know a lot of the kids because, at some point, I was a-- I got to be a part of a-- I was a part of a gang, I guess, is the best way to describe it.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I became the leader of this group of teenagers-- and we were early teens-- which was finally broken up by-- by the police and by some people at the high school finally broke us up.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was involved in that for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think the only reason why I was a part of this gang wasn't because-- was because, once again, it was a way which I was able to survive in a community that was very hostile toward us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But once I was head of the gang, nobody bothered me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The kids left me alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the one thing I did, my mother, when we were very small, she would take us to the library.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'd walk to the library.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was about five blocks away from our house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would get all kinds of books.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I read-- I read-- I think one summer, I must've read 50 books.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
